ContentDesc_Abyssos - Sechster Kreis: You could have sworn that Nemjiji began writing ere you opened your mouth to speak of your battle with Hegemone but pass it off as a unique quirk of the researcher's method of recording dictation. A perusal of her writings afterwards proves to be an exhilarating read, but you wonder whether your account of events was quite so animated...
Instancecontenttextdata_34701_Text: Abyssos is my charge, and I shall not shirk my duty!
Instancecontenttextdata_34703_Text: Be swept away in a flood of aether!
Instancecontenttextdata_34708_Text: Your time draws near. Witness true mastery before your end!
Instancecontenttextdata_34709_Text: Abyssos is my domain! I shall suffer your intrusion no longer!
